OL,3,CPolice appeal after alleged racial
OL,4,Cabuse against player at Rovers match
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for witnesses
OL,7,Fafter Burton Albion defender Udoka
OL,8,FGodwin-Malife was allegedly the target
OL,9,Fof racist abuse during the 3-1 defeat
OL,10,Fby Bristol Rovers at the Memorial
OL,11,FStadium.
OL,13,FBurton boss Gary Bowyer and Godwin-
OL,14,FMalife, 24, were spoken to by
OL,15,Funiformed officers in the changing
OL,16,Froom area as police investigated an
OL,17,Fincident that prompted referee Tom
OL,18,FKirk to halt the game midway through
OL,19,Fthe second half.
