OL,3,CPolice appeal after alleged racial
OL,4,Cabuse against player at Rovers match
OL,6,FDuring a lengthy delay to proceedings,
OL,7,Fa Rovers supporter was ordered to
OL,8,Fleave the ground following the
OL,9,Fincident which prompted a flurry of
OL,10,Ffinger-pointing by players.
OL,12,FAvon and Somerset Police said officers
OL,13,Fwere made aware of the incident at
OL,14,Faround 4:20pm on Saturday.
OL,16,FA fan, who is described as white and
OL,17,Fwearing a black North Face jacket and
OL,18,Fglasses, was seated in the Bristol
OL,19,FRovers section of the stadium when
OL,20,Fthey reportedly made hateful comments.
