OL,3,CPolice appeal after alleged racial
OL,4,Cabuse against player at Rovers match
OL,6,FFootball Officer PC Steven Dix said:
OL,7,F"There is no place for racism in our
OL,8,Fsociety and we will not tolerate such
OL,9,Fbehaviour, and we are conducting a
OL,10,Ffull and thorough investigation.
OL,12,F"We are working closely with both
OL,13,Ffootball clubs to gather statements
OL,14,Ffrom players and have conducted a
OL,15,Fnumber of inquiries, including gaining
OL,16,FCCTV.
