OL,6,FBowyer remained tight-lipped about the
OL,7,Fnature of the incident but told
OL,8,Freporters: "At this moment in time
OL,9,Fthere's not a great deal I can say
OL,10,Fwith an investigation going on and so
OL,11,FI can't really comment on anything
OL,12,Felse other than that at the moment.
OL,14,F"My main concern is the welfare of our
OL,15,Fplayers, so that is the main thing for
OL,16,Fme, making sure all of our players are
OL,17,Fokay, and so we will offer all of them
OL,18,Fthe support that is needed.
OL,26,@pD@LOUvD@AOU
