OL,6,F"But apart from that it is then above
OL,7,Fmy head in terms of the authorities
OL,8,Fand what have you, and it is under
OL,9,Finvestigation."
OL,11,FA statement from Bristol Rovers read:
OL,12,F"Bristol Rovers Football Club is aware
OL,13,Fof an allegation of racist abuse aimed
OL,14,Fat a Burton Albion player during
OL,15,Ftoday's Sky Bet League One fixture at
OL,16,FThe Memorial Stadium.
OL,18,F"The Club is working closely with
OL,19,FBurton Albion and the police to fully
OL,20,Finvestigate the matter.
